s://www.reuters.com/world/russia-warship-conducts-anti-submarine-drill-south-china-sea-agencies-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国推动亚洲股市上涨，红海担忧导致油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-29/</link><description>监管机构周末采取新措施支持市场后，中国股市本周开始领涨亚洲股市。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国医疗器械公司迈瑞计划以9.27亿美元收购亚太医疗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-medical-device-firm-mindray-plans-927-mln-deal-control-apt-medical-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国医疗器械公司深圳迈瑞生物医疗电子表示，计划以 66.5 亿元人民币（9.27 亿美元）的交易获得 APT Medical 的控制权，以扩大心血管疾病相关业务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:58:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-medical-device-firm-mindray-plans-927-mln-deal-control-apt-medical-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>美联储周数据繁忙，美元持稳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-cautious-start-busy-data-fed-week-2024-01-29/</link><description>美元本周开局稳定，因投资者在本周美联储政策会议之前评估美国经济数据，而中东地缘政治紧张局势升级抑制了风险情绪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:46:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-cautious-start-busy-data-fed-week-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>与顶级债权人谈判破裂后恒大面临迫在眉睫的清算 - 华尔街日报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-faces-imminent-liquidation-after-talks-with-top-creditors-break-down-2024-01-29/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周日援引知情人士的话报道，中国房地产开发商恒大集团面临迫在眉睫的清算，因为其海外债权人未能在本周末的第 11 小时内就重组这家规模庞大的房地产公司达成重组协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-faces-imminent-liquidation-after-talks-with-top-creditors-break-down-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将把三大资产管理公司并入中国投资有限责任公司-新华社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-merge-three-major-asset-managers-into-china-investment-corp-xinhua-2024-01-29/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社财经报道，作为金融机构改革计划的一部分，中国计划将国内三大坏账管理公司并入主权财富基金中国投资有限责任公司（CIC）（CIC.UL）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-merge-three-major-asset-managers-into-china-investment-corp-xinhua-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大被勒令清算，欠债3000亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</link><description>香港一家法院周一下令对房地产巨头中国恒大集团进行清算，此举可能会在中国摇摇欲坠的金融市场中引发连锁反应，因为政策制定者正忙于遏制日益加深的危机。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国 PMI 和美联储决定将带来更多欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-28/</link><description>美联储的行动和主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的新闻发布会将主导会议进程。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:49:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美本周将就芬太尼前体化学品问题举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/first-meeting-us-china-working-group-fentanyl-precursor-chemicals-be-held-2024-01-28/</link><description>一位美国高级官员周日表示，中美芬太尼前体化学品工作组首次联席会议将于周二在北京举行。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 14:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/first-meeting-us-china-working-group-fentanyl-precursor-chemicals-be-held-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许菲律宾向争议岛礁派遣部队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</link><description>中国海警表示，已做出“临时特别安排”，允许菲律宾通过一艘停泊在争议礁石上的二战时期船只向部队运送物资。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 13:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国法案提出后，中国华大智造、GemPharmatech 为自己辩护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-mgi-tech-gempharmatech-defend-themselves-after-us-bill-proposed-2024-01-28/</link><description>中国华大智造周日表示，作为基因测序行业的上游设备提供商，在美国拟议的生物安全法案将其名字纳入法案后，其业务不涉及数据收集。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:23:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-mgi-tech-gempharmatech-defend-themselves-after-us-bill-proposed-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道，俄罗斯计划建设的通往中国的天然气管道面临施工延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-planned-gas-pipeline-china-faces-construction-delay-ft-2024-01-28/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周日报道，蒙古总理奥云额尔登表示，俄罗斯计划于今年启动的通往中国的新西伯利亚力量2号天然气管道的建设可能会被推迟。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-planned-gas-pipeline-china-faces-construction-delay-ft-2024-01-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>